{"tid":2455960,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"點解咁高質既漫畫，《關於地球的運動》冇人講","createTime":"2021-03-21T14:01:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T06:04:39.000Z","uid":342887,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0e4440a2ba96bde5fe8c425707af23e6ea9ef32b","tid":2455960,"uid":342887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T14:01:58.000Z","msg":"暫時得5集，結果宜家好想快啲睇更新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n故事背景簡介：故事以15世紀的歐洲作為背景，羅馬天主教以外，或者質疑上帝創世論都會被當作異端思想，不斷被處以火刑的時代。主角神童拉法爾已經預定好了要跳級上大學，而大家也都期待他去專攻當時最為重要的神學。對於最為重視合理性的拉法爾而言這是必然的選擇，只要遵循合理性世界就是易如反掌的。然而某一天，在拉法爾的身邊出現的神秘男人，他所研究的正是在異端思想中最核心的「真理」，地動說。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kCsDrWS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkCsDrWS.jpg&h=9c7f492f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AgXG9ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAgXG9ad.jpg&h=b4d3cc93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xy1s4Jz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxy1s4Jz.jpg&h=4e9107dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea5658b9a457d5b8b1a4274282acea48fa715f22","tid":2455960,"uid":342887,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T14:04:14.000Z","msg":"BTW 呢套喺前日既2021漫畫大賞攞左二獎，只僅次芙莉蓮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"343a1f290f60a4809f26a8980e757ef5e06019ab","tid":2455960,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T14:04:42.000Z","msg":"終於有人譯"},{"pid":"2408e8d03aa6588891fe26e886e072ebb5bff1aa","tid":2455960,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T14:05:29.000Z","msg":"你依家講左了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28de0776329f728f6e3374540747257791686b47","tid":2455960,"uid":342887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2408e8d03aa6588891fe26e886e072ebb5bff1aa","tid":2455960,"uid":8307,"like"